.-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------.

INSTALLATION:

Make sure you have downloaded the latest version of pipsqueek from http://pipsqueek.l8nite.net/

To unpack:
	tar -zxvf pipsqueek-version.tar.gz

To configure:
	Edit data/xml/settings.tidy.xml to suit your preferences.
	When you are done editing, simply copy settings.tidy.xml to settings.xml

To run:
	cd /path/to/pipsqueek-version
	./pipsqueek.pl &> pipsqueek.log &

*IMPORTANT*
The settings file should be self-explanatory.
If not, send email to pipsqueek@l8nite.net, and I will attempt to write some better documentation

.______________________________________________________________________________________________________________.

